    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in fair condition. The exterior has visible scratches and dents that are noticeable but not severe. The interior shows moderate wear including worn upholstery and scuffed trim. Mechanical systems are functional but may have some minor issues. This car is suitable for a buyer looking for basic transportation at a reduced price point.",
      "price": 20000.0,
